    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311230/extras/f56ccaaa3eac765ea43ffed859170211.poster.avif?t=1760907187\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311230/extras/f56ccaaa3eac765ea43ffed859170211.webm?t=1760907187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311230/extras/f56ccaaa3eac765ea43ffed859170211.mp4?t=1760907187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >如果你的宠物猫变成了古埃及神祇，你会怎么做？</h2>在《航程：求职面试模拟器!》中，你将扮演一位穷困潦倒的求职者，在竞争激烈的求职市场中艰难求生，同时还要做出艰难的抉择。幸运的是，你的宠物猫可以帮助你平衡工作与生活！<br><br>《Passage》包含一个超过8小时的分支剧情，原创剧情，原创角色插画，身临其境的原声音乐以及5个独特的结局！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >走进毕业生求职者的世界</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311230/extras/1e1df66c7b43a67dd46b03dc212af12a.poster.avif?t=1760907187\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311230/extras/1e1df66c7b43a67dd46b03dc212af12a.webm?t=1760907187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311230/extras/1e1df66c7b43a67dd46b03dc212af12a.mp4?t=1760907187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在《Passage》中，你是一位刚毕业的大学生，正在拼命地寻找工作。你总是被拒绝的噩梦所困扰——直到有一天，你心爱的猫咪伸出了援手！在他的帮助下，你就能开始挑战公司面试的黑暗世界了——如今，一次面试可能决定生死……<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >给你的新猫神留下深刻印象</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311230/extras/6d99c29f424c7175727479eaa109975f.poster.avif?t=1760907187\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311230/extras/6d99c29f424c7175727479eaa109975f.webm?t=1760907187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311230/extras/6d99c29f424c7175727479eaa109975f.mp4?t=1760907187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你的新朋友不仅能提供建议，他们还有独特的力量来帮助你！他们甚至会为你暂停时间……不过，最好祈祷你的面试技巧能给他们留下深刻印象——世界上的雇主毕竟有限。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >揭开黑暗的秘密</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311230/extras/6089c1346c85e036d93d421dd91c0308.poster.avif?t=1760907187\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311230/extras/6089c1346c85e036d93d421dd91c0308.webm?t=1760907187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311230/extras/6089c1346c85e036d93d421dd91c0308.mp4?t=1760907187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>企业面试的世界可能充满黑暗——许多人因此失去希望，但在我们的帮助下，你一定能成功！在你踏上史诗般的求职之旅时，探索你未来雇主的真相，以及你的噩梦。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >密歇根州和华盛顿州联合制作。</h2>",
